<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">John Tyler Community College</h2>
<strong>Chester, VA</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>AP credit is only awarded to students who are enrolled in classes at John Tyler Community College and are curriculum-placed. For evaluation, students must have official AP score reports forwarded from ETS to the Office of Student Records at JTCC.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.jtcc.edu/downloads/current/student_handbook.pdf" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

